2 way data binding & ng-model
--------------------------------
ng-model ,{{name}}

note:- ng-model can only be used in form elements !!!!!!!!

js
---
let person={
           name:"pranav",
           age:"25"
       }
       $scope.person=person;

html
-----

<input type="text" ng-model="person.name">  //no {{}} needed it checks person.name obj in the specified controller 
<p>{{person.name}}</p> //instantly changes on person.name changes
